						<div class="postbody">There's something weird about the jump... It looks like at one point in the way up it gets an extra boost, and that doesn't look/feel very natural... Maybe this has to do with the way you implemented the variable jump height.
<br />
<br />Other than that, the controls feel OK, better than a lot of commercial NES games (many of them didn't even have any sort of acceleration, inertia, etc). Once you implement platforms we can stand on it will be easier to judge the controls I guess.</div>

